txt.en: Dunlending looters can be found rummaging around near the bodies of the fallen Rohirrim at the Fords of Isen.\n\nYou should drive off Dunlending looters.

Dunlending looters have already begun searching the bodies of the fallen Rohirrim, defiling them where they died.\n\nYou should drive off the looters to show them that Rohan has not yet fallen while the Free Peoples still stand.
Dunlending looters defile the corpses of the noble Rohirrim soldiers who fell at the Fords of Isen.
You have driven off a number of Dunlending looters for the sake of the fallen Rohirrim at the Fords of Isen.
